PP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75481471_221956027020265_990023121912333022_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bmMdmP3JN-wQ7kNvgHfK0h8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCad4WHZ7TtvhMRN2doaBPtOHY2qCfjuxl5PA0kb-gOOA&oe=66F7E2F7"}]}, "id": "675714241062573", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Screenshot 1.png", "id": "841971017268971", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031459_841971020602304_5603721328228463314_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=151IUKbCDx8Q7kNvgGbc8Eu&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA4oyq2BSpx2sz0yMpbfVpzHLP2c0wbJtxhVCO5WHDj5A&oe=66F7DAC2"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot 2.png", "id": "594350042859235", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974868_594350046192568_433296575534262939_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=fzbGYyYCLTcQ7kNvgFQBH4X&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAoxBp6d5ZUGfdJKxz2EatFKq-7iWnHq2DMKE-xD9AXxQ&oe=66F7F852"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot 3.png", "id": "219007137802253", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036664_219007141135586_5891260070562807065_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=36ujwXxp27cQ7kNvgGsnQu6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBqFLUAyZUQWmXpNuhX1e7Uz_ehyQoblAgyyd1eftqJQw&oe=66F8024D"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot 4.png", "id": "1033141091011127", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75210393_1033141094344460_3320745896777132937_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=yCg6-DHHBBcQ7kNvgFtnE8M&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBGWAdKux_zDV1_w4FrirB67-AociZDfjLM4IGCj_-vhg&oe=66F7F995"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot 5.png", "id": "798117928651047", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982617_798117931984380_4157756349900375535_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=R87sXTGNGPwQ7kNvgGkSe_t&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDetTXOghZhz7Wak1ZS2uXT44AblwD1hqCyDQyJ6ILH2g&oe=66F7FD60"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "HereSphere VR Video Player", "keywords": [], "long_description": "HereSphere is a cutting edge VR video player that enhances the immersiveness of stereoscopic VR videos. The comprehensive projection system allows for accurate projection of equirectangular and fisheye videos. Correct lens distortions, camera stereo alignment errors, video stitching and production errors, and even adjust the image to match your IPD, head orientation, and position with a state-of-the-art autofocus depth algorithm. Ever notice double vision when rotating your head while watching stereoscopic VR videos? Autofocus fixes this issue.\n\nHereSphere comes with the following additional features:\n- Play local videos or stream from SMB shares or the web browser\n- Timestamped file tagging system with media library search tools, playlists, and autoseeking that will automatically jump to the desired tags\n- Image sharpening and fine-tuned color adjustments\n- Key-framed settings that can be set to different values for different points in time, allowing the player to load the ideal settings for each scene\n- Simultaneous playback of multiple flat-screen videos, with audio that automatically focuses on the video in front of the viewer\n- Support for external subtitle files (srt, ssa, ass) with automatic depth adjustments for VR videos", "short_description": "The ultimate VR video player for enthusiasts. Packed with features for enhancing immersion, improving clarity, and user customization. Experience VR videos in the highest quality with accurate depth and scale."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://heresphere.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "HereSphere LLC", "support_website_url": "https://heresphere.com/contact-us/", "website_url": "https://heresphere.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "384928226018505"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "568025572165301"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1366489124083450"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1366489124083450"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1690916080, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1366489124083450"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8087997891235939", "version": "0.11.3"}, "id": "284746987408443", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6308914842477595", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8087997891235939"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "284746987408443"}]}, "change_log": "HereSphere update v0.11.3 is now available. This update adds the option to provide script tokens with the HereSphere web API, adds some quality of life features, and fixes some bugs.\n\nScript Tokens:\n- Added a script token url field to the HereSphere web API when requesting video json data. This field should contain a url that will receive a HTTP POST message that contains a \"connectionKey\" field in a json body, and should respond with a \"scriptUrl\" field that contains a script download link with a script token.\n\nQuality of Life Improvements:\n- Added a \"Full side-by-side\" stereoscopic setting and corresponding filename detection (such as \"_LRF\" or \"_SBSF\"). This stereoscopic mode will halve the aspect ratio, so it won't be stretched horizontally.\n- Increased subtitle rendering area for VR videos to show more subtitle lines and prevent subtitles from getting cut off.\n\nBug fixes:\n- Fixed issue with timestamp server not initializing properly when switching profiles.\n- Fixed issue with synchronized peripherals connection keys with 12 character lengths not working.\n", "created_date": 1725317180, "id": "8087997891235939", "version": "0.11.3", "version_code": 17, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6308914842477595", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8087997891235939"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "284746987408443"}]}, "change_log": "- Fixed issue with video player being unable to open new videos after a playback error occurs.", "created_date": 1721342980, "id": "7819055674796830", "version": "0.11.2", "version_code": 16, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6308914842477595", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8087997891235939"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1720905990, "id": "7791354567566941", "version": "0.11.1", "version_code": 15, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6308914842477595", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8087997891235939"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "284746987408443"}]}, "change_log": "HereSphere update v0.11.0 is now available. This update adds support for DLNA streaming, support for more synchronized devices, and some bug fixes\n\nDLNA:\n- Added support for DLNA streaming\n- Click on \"DLNA\" in the left side panel. The player will scan your network for DLNA servers. Click on a DLNA server to browse its contents. Currently, only videos are supported.\n- For scripts, you'll need to place the script file in the \"Interactive\" folder on your Quest local storage, and make sure it matches the title of the video.\n- HSP files will be saved/loaded from the \"HereSphere\" folder on your Quest local storage and need to match the title of the video.\n- Subtitle files (.srt, .ssa, and .ass) need to be stored in the \"HereSphere\" folder on your Quest local storage and match the title of the video. \n\nChanges:\n- Added support for more synchronized peripheral devices\n- Added fields \"resource\" and \"identifier\" to the timestamp server message. \"resource\" contains the actual url/path of the currently playing video file. \"identifier\" contains the scene url when using the HereSphere web API. \n\nBug fixes:\n- Fixed issue with video thumbnails continuing to play in the background when menu is hidden.\n- Fixed issue with buffering not triggering playback suspended/resumed events for synchronized peripherals and the event server\n", "created_date": 1719296554, "id": "7692352460800486", "version": "0.11.0", "version_code": 14, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6308914842477595", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8087997891235939"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1707629141, "id": "7108023639233374", "version": "0.10.4", "version_code": 13, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}